name: Andrew Cumine
body:
### Me:

I am a junior web developer living in London. I have a passion for making things. These are links to my [GitHub](https://github.com/ajcumine), [Twitter](https://twitter.com/AJCumine), [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/ajcumine) and I can be contacted via email at ajcumine@gmail.com

### Things I like:

* Ruby
* TDD
* Rails
* Javascript
* JQuery
* JSON
* CSS
* HTML

### A little about me: 

On the 9th of May 2014 I graduated [Makers Academy](http://www.makersacademy.com), a highly selective, 12 week full-time programme that teaches web development.

Previously I learnt C++ and Matlab while studying for a masters degree in mechanical engineering at Durham University.

### This website:

Built using GitHub Pages, this is a website currently under development and will continually be improved upon.
